Definition: an individual quantity of food or drink taken as part of a meal
Example: the helpings were all small; his portion was larger than hers; there's enough for two servings each
Synonyms: verb, consumption, help, portion, serving, serve, noun, quantity, small_indefinite_quantity, meal, p, an, individual, of, food, or, drink, taken, as, part, a, the, helpings, were, all, small, his, was, larger, than, hers, there, s, enough, for, two, servings, each
Category: noun.food
